# 🏛️ Governance

This folder defines the DAO-based governance structure of BUCCONOMICS.

# Key Governance Concepts
- Quadratic voting with emergency veto mechanism
- Reputation-based influence score
- Multi-tier DAO (Local, Regional, National)
- Community proposal process
- Governance token logic

# File Types
- Governance models (markdown & diagrams)
- Voting contracts (linked from `/contracts`)
- Legal interpretation memos (in `/docs`)

> Join the `#governance` discussion in GitHub Discussions to help shape this.
